queries.query: INSERT INTO `api_accesslogs` (`vIPAddress`, `vAPIName`, `vAPIURL`, `dAccessDate`, `vPlatform`, `vBrowser`, `vFileName`) VALUES ('103.105.108.223', 'user_login_email', 'http://18.211.58.235/canoodle/WS/user_login_email', '2020-10-30 14:12:49', 'Unknown OS Platform', 'Unknown Browser', 'user_login_email-1604067169.json')

SELECT `u`.`iUserId` AS `u_user_id`,`u`.`vFirstName` AS `u_first_name`,`u`.`vLastName` AS `u_last_name`,`u`.`vUserName` AS `u_user_name`,`u`.`vEmail` AS `u_email`,`u`.`vMobileNo` AS `u_mobile_no`,`u`.`vProfileImage` AS `u_profile_image`,`u`.`dDob` AS `u_dob`,`u`.`tAddress` AS `u_address`,`u`.`vCity` AS `u_city`,`u`.`dLatitude` AS `u_latitude`,`u`.`dLongitude` AS `u_longitude`,`u`.`iStateId` AS `u_state_id`,`u`.`vStateName` AS `u_state`,`u`.`vZipCode` AS `u_zip_code`,`u`.`eEmailVerified` AS `u_email_verified`,`u`.`eDeviceType` AS `u_device_type`,`u`.`vDeviceModel` AS `u_device_model`,`u`.`vDeviceOS` AS `u_device_os`,`u`.`vDeviceToken` AS `u_device_token`,`u`.`eStatus` AS `u_status`,`u`.`vGender` AS `u_gender`,`u`.`iAge` AS `u_age`,`u`.`dtAddedAt` AS `u_added_at`,`u`.`dtUpdatedAt` AS `u_updated_at`,('15dfc459b45e34ff596855f619b758c6aa7b579e962aa46d37503c7417cb61a9') AS auth_token1,`u`.`eSocialLoginType` AS `u_social_login_type`,`u`.`vSocialLoginId` AS `u_social_login_id`,`u`.`ePushNotify` AS `u_push_notify`,`u`.`eOneTimeTransaction` AS `e_one_time_transaction`,`u`.`tOneTimeTransaction` AS `t_one_time_transaction`,`u`.`vTermsConditionsVersion` AS `u_terms_conditions_version`,`u`.`vPrivacyPolicyVersion` AS `u_privacy_policy_version`,(concat(u.vFirstName,' ',u.vLastName)) AS email_user_name,`u`.`eLogStatus` AS `u_log_status_updated`,`u`.`eIsSubscribed` AS `u_is_subscribed`,`u`.`tReceiptData` AS `u_receipt_data`,`u`.`vSubscriptionId` AS `u_subscription_id`,`p`.`iPetId` AS `pet_id`,`p`.`vPetName` AS `pet_name`,`p`.`vBreed` AS `breed`,`p`.`vPetAge` AS `pet_age`,`p`.`vPetCategory` AS `pet_category`,`p`.`vPetDescription` AS `pet_description`,`p`.`vAKCRegistered` AS `akc_registered` FROM `users` AS `u` LEFT JOIN `pet` AS `p` ON `p`.`iUserId` = `u`.`iUserId` WHERE u.iUserId='13'  LIMIT 1
